description:
Paradice Seeker was the most popular game in the world. It was a golden monarch that dominated the gaming market and economy. 

Never again will I allow him to treat me like a dog. 

The legendary title he would gain in the future, as well as all the money he would earn, are all in my memory.

‘I will take it all away from him’.

T/N: Paradice Seeker is the name of the game and that is how it is spelled.>
